{"tid":1846820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"來吧!大混亂! 期待手持午餐肉就有西屌的日子!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2020-01-27T17:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T22:31:11.000Z","uid":79793,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"caec540d25f761008ba1c35ff3063251180ba6b2","tid":1846820,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:58:27.000Z","msg":"北韓開戰又好,侵侵炸鳩敘利亞又好,IS恐怖襲擊又好,武漢肺炎又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使講<br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B5dF7m9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB5dF7m9.jpg&h=4717ea87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1R8wOR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1R8wOR.png&h=ea8d38c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyTritV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyTritV.png&h=5a9f9e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6d7e6d029bee108d37183e1ffa66f95a69c2c0","tid":1846820,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:58:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94ef336d7d8ac4ddc35c82d14fd91aa97c63ac23","tid":1846820,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:01:51.000Z","msg":"有改內容 冇新圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc762885ce0764fb9b693123a32c33f75828abd4","tid":1846820,"uid":185589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94ef336d7d8ac4ddc35c82d14fd91aa97c63ac23","tid":1846820,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:01:51.000Z","msg":"有改內容 冇新圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:03:19.000Z","msg":"可能啲嘢根本無郁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfb78b659d6d0e123cda26421c640373c232ece","tid":1846820,"uid":190401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:14:01.000Z","msg":"你估人地唔識來搶咩，到時你好打過葉問都無用。"},{"pid":"3d98eaaf944aa15a43127075bb7aed38fb76aa07","tid":1846820,"uid":28437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:15:25.000Z","msg":"兒登仔有幾多人識依段野都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1bd0f892851e37b51